	~%-100%λυθείην#Incorrect. The form for aorist passive optative 1st sing. of the verb “I loosen” is **λυθείην** (Ch. 4).
	~%100%πολιτῶν#Correct: **πολιτῶν** is the correct form for gen. pl. of the noun “citizen” (Chapter 4).
	~%-100%πέμψω#Incorrect. The form for future active indicative 1st sing. of the verb “I send” is **πέμψω** (Ch. 3).
	~%-100%ἐκεκελεύκαμεν#Incorrect. The form for pluperfect active indicative 1st pl. of the verb “I order” is **ἐκεκελεύκαμεν** (Ch. 3).
	~%-100%παιδεύεις#Incorrect. The form for present active indicative 2nd sing. of the verb “I educate” is **παιδεύεις** (Ch. 2).
}


